data.description: OPEN HOUSE 1/21/24 FROM 12-2 P.M. Nestled in the community of Taylor, this ranch-style home offers a perfect blend of comfort and modernity. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom, this residence has been tastefully updated, presenting a move-in-ready opportunity for its new owners. Step into a welcoming atmosphere adorned with freshly painted interiors, it is both clean and inviting. The updated kitchen and bathroom showcase contemporary features. Outside you will find a fenced yard, shed and covered pergola providing a safe and private space. A shed adds convenience, offering ample storage for tools and outdoor essentials, keeping your space organized and clutter-free. Don't miss out on the chance to make this updated and move-in-ready ranch-style home yours. Schedule a tour today and envision the lifestyle that awaits in this cozy and refreshed home! Certificate of Occupancy will be provided by the seller.
